cial occasion. I walked away feeling like nothing was too much trouble and that as they wanted my time in their care to be one i 'd not forget and you know what they got it right.....every last detail. Mark K hotel manager i know that you will read this, please extend my thanks to your team for making my birthday in Dubai one i will cherish forever.	
