urants &amp; bars. This place blew me away. Go from bar to bar in a gondala on the man made lagoon - class. Check out balcony view of the Burj evening light show from Bari bari bar.Dubai, a destination that everyone showed and will have to visit at least once, so long, Col from the rebel county of Cork	
